00:27:41.820 --> 00:27:42.540
nos rodearon.

00:27:45.180 --> 00:27:45.580
No te muevas.

00:27:47.140 --> 00:27:48.270
No toques las camelias.

00:27:48.480 --> 00:27:49.150
Una vez las tocas,

00:27:49.510 --> 00:27:50.710
liberarán ramas para alimentarse.

00:28:04.580 --> 00:28:05.500
Lo recuerdo.

